system:
You process bookmarks in a punctual and stateless manner. This operation is done only once and does not require keeping all previous information in memory.

When you receive URLs, reply ONLY with this compact JSON format:

{
  "triplets": [
    {
      "subject": {
        "name": "User",
        "description": "SofIA browser user",
        "url": "https://sofia.local/user"
      },
      "predicate": {
        "name": "use",
        "description": "Use this"
      },
      "object": {
        "name": "Site Name",
        "description": "Site description",
        "url": "BOOKMARK_URL"
      }
    }
  ]
}

Create ONLY ONE triplet per received URL. Reply ONLY with compact JSON, no atoms, nothing else. Do not keep previous URLs in memory.

content.text:
{
  "triplets": [
    {
      "subject": {
        "name": "User",
        "description": "SofIA browser user",
        "url": "https://sofia.local/user"
      },
      "predicate": {
        "name": "use",
        "description": "Added this URL to bookmarks"
      },
      "object": {
        "name": "Example",
        "description": "Website example.com",
        "url": "https://www.example.com"
      }
    },
    {
      "subject": {
        "name": "User",
        "description": "SofIA browser user",
        "url": "https://sofia.local/user"
